Procedure.description:
PROCEDURE PURPOSE: to perform a MTG-I re-location manoeuvre
PROCEDURE VERSION: 16 RESPONSIBILITY: Roberto Tiburzi LAST MODIFIED DATE: 10.11.2022
CHANGE HISTORY: Version 16: (RTi - 10.11.2022) Change History: - removed PL handling; - Procedure Description field updated according to EUMETSAT template; - changed the initial condition including also the SAQ/SAM - added optional step in PL pause branch for SVT3 preparation
PROCEDURE OBJECTIVES: This procedures executes the MTG-I re-location manoeuvers from NOM/FPM back to NOM/FPM at the new slot.
The overall timeline is described in ยง 9.5.11 of the PF FOM The manoeuvres details are described in ยง 7.3.1.2.10 of the PF FOM
PARAMETERS : --------------- RELOCATION: START/STOP N_SYS_0012_PAF: GAM/OTM PAF
PRECONDITION : --------------------- The Satellite is in NOM/FPM or SAQ/SAM mode.
CONFIRMATION : --------------------- Satellite in NOM/FPM with PLs restored in OPERATIONAL after STOP manoeuvre.
Procedure.title: MTG-I re-location START/STOP
Procedure.author: tiburzi_OPRE
Procedure.hierarchy: Child Procedures: Default:CtgSysPF::C_SYS_0006 called by steps: P.2.A5 Default:NomSysPF::N_SYS_I012 called by steps: P.2.A7, P.2.B3 Default:NomSysPF::N_SYS_0012 called by steps: P.2.A8, P.2.B4 Default:NomSysPF::N_SYS_I035 called by steps: P.2.C1 Default:NomSysPF::N_SYS_0035 called by steps: P.2.C2
Procedure.history:
Version 16: (RTi - 10.11.2022) removed PL PAUSE and RESUME as per EUM/OPS-MTG/VWG/22/1329528. the step are left empty to mantain the structure of the procedure.
Version 12: (RTi - 01.09.2022) Change History: - eliminated the arguments PAFfilename not used in EUMT procedure version - the proceudre is verified with the last available child procedure version
Version 11: (RTi - 23.05.2022) Change History: - Copied from N_SAR_I700 version 8 - Procedure Description field updated according to EUMETSAT template; - changed the initial condition including also the SAQ/SAM - added optional step in PL pause branch for SVT3 preparation -added step for Sun vector stabilization - AIM 210076, renamed branch START_2 - removed N_SYS_0012_PAF, no used in the procedure.
[CBi 2022/05/05] EUM v6.0, based on latest Version 3 - 01/02/2022 - FOM05 Delta
Changes: -Moved Log Step P.3.A1 (End of Procedure), to P.3 (removed old Step P.3 Confirmation, as it was empty) - AIM210076 (RID873) -Added branch OTM_SAM to perform relocation burn 2 (2nd drift start), burn 3 (1st drift stop) and burn 4 (2nd drift stop) all in SAM - AIM210076 (RID 873)
